{"tid":1792120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"尖咀海港城係九倉集團架，防暴同便衣狗自由出入兼拉人打人都唔理","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T11:41:25.000Z","uid":104922,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"37e89fb8cdad07eeaa0a63be47831c3e5814035c","tid":1792120,"uid":104922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4bSr12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4bSr12.jpg&h=d6e6e463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有朋友發夢見到，今日全日都無見過任何保安係商場內扮下野睇水，任啲蒙面恐怖份子橫行商場，最後拒絕出示委任證嘅恐怖份子拉埋人，綠曱甴衝入商場增援，趕人放椒再推跌哂啲人，商場保安/職員完全無出過黎維持商場秩序/詢問疑似警員衝入商場嘅原因/要求出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n雖然以家大家習慣左地產商與狗同行，但我係絕對唔會忘記你地呢班發展商就係屠殺港人嘅幫兇！連保障顧客係商場內嘅安全都做唔到，就咪撚開門做生意！<br />\n<br />\n清算之日，一定會清算埋你地！<br />\n<br />\nP.S 攬炒同學界團隊，可唔可以加埋啲地產商高層落清算名單？"},{"pid":"5d5baba62881ea35d3a5fb5739f02b54991765f9","tid":1792120,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Ap4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=c478f6a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Ap4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=f1c7de67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"bdf46e5ef77873f